'''Ramin Rezaeian Semeskandi''' ({{langx|fa|رامین رضائیان سمسکندی}}; born 21 March 1990) is an Iranian professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[defender (association football)|defender]] for [[Persian Gulf Pro League]] club [[Esteghlal F.C.|Esteghlal]] and the [[Iran national football team|Iran national team]].

He started his career as a [[right-back]], but he often plays as a [[winger (association football)|winger]]. Rezaeian was [[Carlos Queiroz]]'s first choice on the right side of the defence of the [[Iran national football team|Iran men's national team]] in the [[2018 FIFA World Cup qualification]] matches. Known for his great speed, agility, and athleticism, he is often regarded as one of Iran's best ever fullbacks.

==Early life==
Rezaeian was born in [[Semes Kandeh-ye Olya]], a village in [[Sari County]], [[Mazandaran Province|Mazanderan]].<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.iribnews.ir/fa/news/2152320/ملی-پوشان-مازندرانی-در-پی-درخشش-در-جام-جهانی-فوتبال |title=ملی پوشان مازندرانی در پی درخشش در جام جهانی فوتبال |trans-title=Mazanderani national players looking for a shine at the Football World Cup |language=fa |access-date=5 October 2018 |work=IRIB News}}</ref>

==Club career==
===Saba Qom===
Rezaeian played his entire career for [[Saba Qom F.C.|Saba Qom]] before signing for [[Rah Ahan Tehran F.C.|Rah Ahan]] in 2013.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.iplstats.com/playersteam12.htm |title=Iranian Premier League Stats: 2018-2019 Season |work=IPLstats.com |access-date=5 October 2018}}</ref> He made 98 appearances for the club scoring seven goals.

===Rah Ahan===
Rezaeian signed a three–year with the [[Tehran]]-based club [[Rah Ahan Tehran F.C.|Rah Ahan]] in 2013. After several good performances in the [[2014–15 Persian Gulf Pro League|2014–15]] season, Rezaeian was recognized as one of the best fullbacks in the league and was called up to the national team. On 3 April 2015, Rezaeian scored his team's first goal in a 2–2 draw against [[Persepolis F.C.|Persepolis]]. Two weeks later, on 17 April, he scored a brace in a 2–2 draw against [[Esteghlal Khuzestan F.C.|Esteghlal Khuzestan]].
[[File:Esteghlal FC vs Al-Gharafa FC, 16 September 2024 - 08.jpg|thumb|Esteghlal FC vs Al-Gharafa FC]]

===Persepolis===
Rezaeian joined [[Persepolis F.C.|Persepolis]] on 27 June 2015 with a two-year contract.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://fc-perspolis.com/Contents/2755/بازیکن-تیم-ملی-فوتبال-ایران-سرخپوش-شد |title=بازیکن تیم ملی فوتبال ایران سرخپوش شد |trans-title=Iran national team player became a red-wearer |language=fa |work=FC-Perspolis.com |access-date=5 October 2018}}</ref> He scored his first goal for Persepolis in a 2–0 victory against [[Siah Jamegan F.C.|Siah Jamegan]]. On 26 December 2015, Rezaeian scored a 30-yard free kick against [[Padideh F.C.|Padideh]] in stoppage time to earn them a 2–2 draw. After initially signing a contract with Turkish [[Süper Lig]] club [[Çaykur Rizespor|Rizespor]] in the summer of 2016,<ref>{{cite web|url=http://footballitarin.com/link_page.php?id=238442|title=فوتبالی‌ترین - پاسخ منفی رضاییان به پیشنهاد تیم ترکیه‌ای|website=footballitarin.com}}</ref> Rezaeian cancelled his contract and re–joined [[Persepolis F.C.|Persepolis]].

===Oostende===
After rejecting an offer from Tehran rivals [[Esteghlal F.C.]], Rezaeian joined Belgian club [[K.V. Oostende]] on 9 July 2017 with a two-year contract after a successful trial period at the club. Ramin made his debut on 27 July 2017 in a 3rd round [[UEFA Europa League|Europa League]] qualifier against French club [[Olympique de Marseille]]. Oostende lost the match 4–2 and Rezaeian played the full 90 minutes.

===Al Shahania===

On 6 November 2018, Rezaeian joined [[Qatar Stars League]] side [[Al-Shahania SC|Al Shahania]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.tasnimnews.com/en/news/2018/11/06/1869971/qatar-s-al-shahania-signs-iranian-ramin-rezaeian|title=Qatar's Al Shahania Signs Iranian Ramin Rezaeian|website=tasnimnews.com|date=6 November 2018|access-date=6 November 2018}}</ref> In his first match with the club, on 8 November, Ramin scored a free kick goal in his team's 5–1 loss to [[Al-Duhail SC|Al Duhail]]. On 23 November, in his second match with his club, Ramin assisted his team's only goal in a 1–0 win against [[Al-Kharitiyath]].

===Al-Duhail===

On 22 August 2020, Rezaeian signed a two-year contract with [[Qatar Stars League]] champion, [[Al-Duhail SC|Al-Duhail]].<ref>{{Cite web |date=23 August 2020 |title=Al-Duhail signs Iranian winger Ramin Rezaeian |url=https://en.mehrnews.com/news/162614/Al-Duhail-signs-Iranian-winger-Ramin-Rezaeian |access-date=10 July 2022 |website=Mehr News Agency |language=en}}</ref>

===Al-Sailiya===

After the engagement of the new trainer from Al-Duhail, Rezaein was loaned to Al-Sailiya.<ref>{{Cite web |date=1 January 2021 |title=Ramin Rezaeian joins Al Sailiya club |url=https://www.tehrantimes.com/news/456446/Ramin-Rezaeian-joins-Al-Sailiya-club |access-date=10 July 2022 |website=Tehran Times |language=en}}</ref>

=== Persepolis ===
On 12 February 2022, Rezaeian signed a contract with [[Persian Gulf Pro League]] champions [[Persepolis F.C.|Persepolis]].<ref>{{Cite web|title=رسمی؛ رامین رضاییان به پرسپولیس پیوست (عکس)|url=https://www.varzesh3.com/news/1810368|access-date=12 February 2022|website=ورزش سه|language=fa}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=رامین رضاییان رسماً به پرسپولیس برگشت- اخبار فوتبال ایران - اخبار ورزشی تسنیم {{!}} Tasnim|url=https://www.tasnimnews.com/fa/news/1400/11/23/2661808|access-date=12 February 2022|website=خبرگزاری تسنیم {{!}} Tasnim|language=fa}}</ref>

=== Sepahan ===
On 15 July 2022, Rezaeian signed a contract with Persian Gulf Pro League side [[Sepahan S.C.|Sepahan]].<ref>{{Cite web |title=رضاییان به سپاهان پیوست (عکس) |url=https://www.varzesh3.com/news/1833674/%D8%B1%D8%B6%D8%A7%DB%8C%DB%8C%D8%A7%D9%86-%D8%A8%D9%87-%D8%B3%D9%BE%D8%A7%D9%87%D8%A7%D9%86-%D9%BE%DB%8C%D9%88%D8%B3%D8%AA-%D8%B9%DA%A9%D8%B3 |access-date=15 July 2022 |website=ورزش سه |language=fa}}</ref>
[[File:Esteghlal 0 - 0 Al Nassr, round of 16 of the AFC Elite League, Azadi Stadium, 3 March 2025 15.jpg|thumb|match between Esteghlal of Iran and Al-Nassr of Saudi Arabia]]

=== Esteghlal ===
In December 2024 while with [[Esteghlal F.C.|Esteghlal]], Rezaeian was summoned by [[Football Federation Islamic Republic of Iran]] after hugging a female fan, months after goalkeeper [[Hossein Hosseini (footballer, born 1992)|Hossein Hosseini]] was also summoned by the federation and faced a suspension and fine for embracing a female fan in April 2024.<ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.iranintl.com/en/202412271105 | title=Iran football federation summons player after hugging female fan | website=Iran International }}</ref> In his first game for Esteghlal against [[Shams Azar F.C.|Shams Azar]] in [[Qazvin]], he changed the outcome of the game in favor of Esteghlal with an assist to [[Mohammad Hossein Eslami]] in the final minutes, and the game ended with a 2-1 victory for Esteghlal.<ref>{{Cite web |title=نقش پررنگ رامین رضاییان در برتری استقلال؛ آقای سوپراستار وارد می‌شود |url=https://football360.ir/post/20240816179/%D9%86%D9%82%D8%B4-%D9%BE%D8%B1%D8%B1%D9%86%DA%AF-%D8%B1%D8%A7%D9%85%DB%8C%D9%86-%D8%B1%D8%B6%D8%A7%DB%8C%DB%8C%D8%A7%D9%86-%D8%AF%D8%B1-%D8%A8%D8%B1%D8%AA%D8%B1%DB%8C-%D8%A7%D8%B3%D8%AA%D9%82%D9%84%D8%A7%D9%84-%D8%A2%D9%82%D8%A7%DB%8C-%D8%B3%D9%88%D9%BE%D8%B1%D8%A7%D8%B3%D8%AA%D8%A7%D8%B1-%D9%88%D8%A7%D8%B1%D8%AF-%D9%85%DB%8C%D8%B4%D9%88%D8%AF |access-date=2025-04-27 |website=فوتبال 360}}</ref> Rezaian played in his second game for Esteghlal against [[Malavan F.C.|Malavan]] in Qazvin and managed to score two goals from the penalty spot for the Blues, and in addition to his first goal for Esteghlal, he was named the best player on the field.<ref>{{Cite AV media |url=https://video.varzesh3.com/video/351040/%D8%AE%D9%84%D8%A7%D8%B5%D9%87-%D8%A8%D8%A7%D8%B2%DB%8C-%D8%A7%D8%B3%D8%AA%D9%82%D9%84%D8%A7%D9%84-2-%D9%85%D9%84%D9%88%D8%A7%D9%86-2 |title=خلاصه بازی استقلال 2 - ملوان 2- ویدیو ورزش سه |date=2024-08-23 |type=Video |language=fa |publisher=ویدیو ورزش سه |access-date=2025-04-27}}</ref> He also managed to register an assist in [[Tehran Derby]].

Her first Asian goal with Esteghlal came against Qatar's [[Al-Gharafa SC|Al-Gharafa]] in the [[AFC Champions League Elite]], and on the day Esteghlal defeated their Qatari rival 3-0, he also scored one of these goals, making it her first Asian goal with the Iranian blue team.<ref>{{Cite AV media |url=https://video.varzesh3.com/video/353172/%D8%AD%D8%B1%DA%A9%D8%AA-%D8%AF%DB%8C%D8%AF%D9%86%DB%8C-%D8%B1%D8%A7%D9%85%DB%8C%D9%86-%DA%AF%D9%84-%D8%AF%D9%88%D9%85-%D8%A7%D8%B3%D8%AA%D9%82%D9%84%D8%A7%D9%84-%D8%A8%D9%87-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%BA%D8%B1%D8%A7%D9%81%D9%87 |title=حرکت دیدنی رامین؛ گل دوم استقلال به الغرافه- ویدیو ورزش سه |date=2024-09-16 |type=Video |language=fa |publisher=ویدیو ورزش سه |access-date=2025-04-27 }}</ref>

She also scored her first goal for Esteghlal in the [[Iranian Hazfi Cup|Hazfi Cup]], where she scored in extra time for Esteghlal in the round of 16 of the Hazfi Cup against [[Shams Azar F.C.|Shams Azar]].<ref>{{Cite web |title=گل دوم استقلال به شمس آذر (رامین رضاییان) |url=https://footballi.net/video/935503/%DA%AF%D9%84-%D8%AF%D9%88%D9%85-%D8%A7%D8%B3%D8%AA%D9%82%D9%84%D8%A7%D9%84-%D8%A8%D9%87-%D8%B4%D9%85%D8%B3-%D8%A2%D8%B0%D8%B1-%D8%B1%D8%A7%D9%85%DB%8C%D9%86-%D8%B1%D8%B6%D8%A7%DB%8C%DB%8C%D8%A7%D9%86 |access-date=2025-04-27 |website=فوتبالی |language=fa}}</ref>

==International career==
[[File:Iran and Portugal match at the FIFA World Cup 2018 6.jpg|thumb|Rezaeian (in white) at the [[2018 FIFA World Cup]] ([[Iran national football team|Iran]]–[[Portugal national football team|Portugal]] match)]]
He was called into [[Iran national football team|Iran]]'s [[2015 AFC Asian Cup]] squad on 30 December 2014 by [[Carlos Queiroz]].<ref name="2015acsquad">{{cite web |url=http://www.afcasiancup.com/news/en/nekounam-headlines-iranian-squad/10ppu97hz8lxf1ik1ux49b1ve0 |title=Queiroz Names Team Melli Squad |access-date=30 December 2014 |work=AFCAsianCup.com |archive-date=1 January 2015 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150101072926/http://www.afcasiancup.com/news/en/nekounam-headlines-iranian-squad/10ppu97hz8lxf1ik1ux49b1ve0 |url-status=dead }}</ref> He made his debut against [[Iraq]] in a friendly on 4 January 2015. He also played a friendly match against [[Sweden men's national football team|Sweden]]. Rezaeian scored his first international goal on 17 November 2015 in a 6–0 victory against [[Guam national football team|Guam]]. In May 2018, he was named in [[Iran national football team|Iran's preliminary squad]] for the [[2018 FIFA World Cup]] in Russia.<ref>{{cite news |work=BBC |date=4 June 2018 |access-date=5 October 2018 |title=World Cup 2018: All the confirmed squads for this summer's finals in Russia |url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/44083365}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |title=Queiroz names Iran World Cup squad |language=en-GB |work=BBC Sport |url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/44357568 |access-date=10 July 2022}}</ref>

===2021===

Despite his good performances, he was not invited to the national team.

===2022===

Rezaeian was called up to the squad for the [[2022 FIFA World Cup]] in [[Qatar]].

In the group stage match against [[Wales national football team|Wales]] at the [[Ahmad bin Ali Stadium]] on 25 November 2022, Rezaeian scored the second goal to secure 2–0 victory for Iran.

== Style of play ==
Rezaeian has a high-level skill in long and fast starts.<ref>{{Cite web |last=اسپورت |first=آی |title=تفاوت سبک محرمی و رضاییان: بازی در فضا |url=http://isport.ir/fa/content/9b1d8907401d |access-date=10 July 2022 |website=آی اسپورت |language=fa}}</ref> He has a high skill in long passes and [[Corner kick|corner]] and [[Free kick (association football)|free kicks]]. He also has good scoring skills.<ref>{{Cite web |date=16 February 2022 |title=ببینید {{!}} آنالیز جذاب عملکرد رضاییان؛ چرا جذب رامین برای پرسپولیس حیاتی بود؟ |url=https://www.khabaronline.ir/news/1603475/ببینید-آنالیز-جذاب-عملکرد-رضاییان-چرا-جذب-رامین-برای-پرسپولیس |access-date=10 July 2022 |website=خبرآنلاین |language=fa}}</ref>

[[BBC Persian]] wrote about him: "On the right side, Ramin Rezaeian is the key player of [[Branko Ivanković|Branko]]. He is considered Branko's savior with his scoring power in difficult situations."<ref>{{Cite web |date=1 February 2016 |title=لیگ برتر فوتبال ایران؛ جدال کروات‌ها در ورزشگاه آزادی |url=https://www.bbc.com/persian/sport/2016/02/160201_l51_ipl_football_week18 |access-date=10 July 2022 |website=BBC News فارسی |language=fa}}</ref>

== Personal life ==
[[File:Iran national football team at Airport 05.jpg|thumb|Rezaeian and fans in [[Tehran]] in 2019]]
He is popular among Iranian football fans, especially Persepolis fans.<ref>{{Cite web |date=10 July 2022 |title=چند دلیل برای بازگشت رامین رضاییان به پرسپولیس؛ از چراغ سبز یحیی تا آخرین فرصت حضور در جام جهانی |url=https://www.mizan.news/790968/%da%86%d9%86%d8%af-%d8%af%d9%84%db%8c%d9%84-%d8%a8%d8%b1%d8%a7%db%8c-%d8%a8%d8%a7%d8%b2%da%af%d8%b4%d8%aa-%d8%b1%d8%a7%d9%85%db%8c%d9%86-%d8%b1%d8%b6%d8%a7%db%8c%db%8c%d8%a7%d9%86-%d8%a8%d9%87-%d9%be/ |access-date=10 July 2022 |website=قوه قضائیه {{!}} خبرگزاری میزان {{!}} Mizan Online News Agency |language=fa}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |title=رامین رضاییان و قرمزترین حالت ممکن |language=fa |work=خبرگزاری ایلنا |url=https://www.ilna.ir/fa/tiny/news-1164149 |access-date=10 July 2022}}</ref> His father is a retired doctor and he has only one older sister. Among football players, he is interested in Iranian legend, [[Ali Karimi]]. He has announced that he controls his diet and loves ice cream.<ref>{{Cite web |last=فتوکده |date=22 July 2020 |title=بیوگرافی رامین رضاییان (بازیکن فوتبال) با عکس جدید آماندا |url=https://photokade.com/بیوگرافی-رامین-رضاییان/ |access-date=10 July 2022 |language=fa-IR}}</ref>

On 23 January 2026, in his first game for Foolad, Rezaeian wore black wristbands in solidarity with protesters killed during the [[2025–2026 Iranian protests]].<ref>https://www.iranintl.com/202601225284</ref> The next day, he was summoned by the [[Football Federation Islamic Republic of Iran]] for this action.<ref>https://www.iranintl.com/202601245390</ref> He had previously refused to celebrate a goal he scored against [[Wales national football team|Wales]] during the [[2022 FIFA World Cup]] in solidarity with the [[Mahsa Amini protests]].

